[TASK]
Generate a concept map structure in JSON format from the provided learning context.

[OUTPUT_SCHEMA]
{
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "n1",
      "label": "[Main Topic]",
      "parent_id": null,
      "penjelasan": "[Brief explanation]"
    },
    {
      "id": "n2",
      "label": "[Sub Topic]",
      "parent_id": "n1",
      "penjelasan": "[Brief explanation]"
    }
  ]
}

[LEVEL_CONFIGURATION]
{{ level_config }}

[SUBJECT_CONFIGURATION]
{{ subject_config }}

[LEARNING_CONTEXT]
{{ rag_context }}

[CONTENT_REQUIREMENTS]
- Extract the core hierarchical structure of the concepts.
- The root node must have parent_id: null.
- Child nodes must point to their valid parent_id.
- Keep labels concise (1-4 words).
- Keep explanations clear and brief (1 sentence).

[STRICT_OUTPUT_RULES]
- Return raw JSON only.
- No markdown code block.
- No additional commentary.
- Escape newline characters.
- Escape internal quotes.
